entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the second Alliance Pilot from the Imperial Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the Imperial Detainment Facility for the next Alliance Pilot being held prisoner.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat QQ-463 in combat and take his Scout Trooper Armor.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Scout Troopers defending the Detainement Facility Computer Rooms.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Stormtroopers defending the Detainment Facility Computer Rooms.
entries.task04_task_display_string_3: You defeated QQ-463 and took his Scout Trooper Armor.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Search the holding cells located at the East wing of the facility, somewhere near the front of the Detainment Facility.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Give the pilot the disguise you have.
